title: Help Brie Larson Archives keep their site!
body:
The biggest Brie Larson fansite outside of Tumblr is struggling to maintain their website and they need your help. Keeping an fansite up and updated takes a lot of time and, specially, money. Us from Brie Larson Daily deeply appreciate their hardwork so we wanted to signal boost this message.

If you wish to donate, please contact the admin on Tumblr, Twitter or send an e-mail to brielarsonarchives@gmail.com. All help is appreciated! Thank you.

body:
Captain Marvel Projected to Have Massive Opening Weekend with $140 Million Plus

Marvel Studios and Disney might have another box office juggernaut on their hand with recent projections indicating Captain Marvel could bring in $140 million or more on opening weekend.

Last week, Fandango reported that Captain Marvel was the third highest selling Marvel Cinematic Universe movie in the first 24 hours behind Avengers: Infinity War and Black Panther.
